A bit cheesy sometimes, but overall, they're pretty great.

01:10:15.569 --> 01:10:20.489
That night, they didn't lecture us.

01:10:20.489 --> 01:10:25.489
They just reminded us of one thing and it was pretty deep.

01:10:25.489 --> 01:10:32.489
When we dedicate our lives to Jehovah, our lives includes everything.

01:10:32.489 --> 01:10:38.489
Our time, our resources, our home, our kitchen.

01:10:38.489 --> 01:10:40.489
Yes, our kitchen.

01:10:40.489 --> 01:10:45.489
And how we care for those things, it reflects on him.

01:10:45.489 --> 01:10:48.489
And on us as your parents.

01:10:48.489 --> 01:10:50.489
That kind of sank in.

01:10:50.489 --> 01:10:53.489
I knew I could do better.

