Oh, yeah, we got this.

01:11:01.489 --> 01:11:16.399
Did you notice how the daughters showed respect for their parents?

01:11:16.399 --> 01:11:21.399
They did this by listening and obeying their instructions.

01:11:21.399 --> 01:11:23.399
What was the key?

01:11:23.399 --> 01:11:25.399
It's how they viewed their parents.

01:11:25.399 --> 01:11:30.399
They reflected on their parents' fine example in the ministry at home

01:11:30.399 --> 01:11:34.399
when they would take the time and have the patience to help them,

01:11:34.399 --> 01:11:36.399
to listen to them.

01:11:36.399 --> 01:11:42.399
And they saw the joy on their mother's face as she kept the home clean and tidy.

01:11:42.399 --> 01:11:44.399
What a good example.

01:11:44.399 --> 01:11:50.399
They listened to their parents' advice and then they made personal application.

01:11:50.399 --> 01:11:55.399
They learned that showing respect into family meant helping out with chores,

01:11:55.399 --> 01:11:58.399
even when it meant doing the dishes.

01:11:58.399 --> 01:12:03.399
This made their parents happy and the daughters happy as well.

